Plug jocelynmallon/zshmarks horosgrisa/zsh-completions voronkovich/gitignore.plugin.zsh zsh-users/zsh-syntax-highlighting horosgrisa/zsh-history-substring-search horosgrisa/zsh-autosuggestions horosgrisa/autoenv horosgrisa/fasd  horosgrisa/mysql-colorize horosgrisa/zsh-konsole-theme-changer

Plug sickill/bitpocket horosgrisa/shipit

